snippet.title: 1 Year For KGF Chapter 2 | Yash | Prashanth Neel | Vijay Kiragandur | Sanjay Dutt | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
One year ago today, #KGFChapter2 took us on an unforgettable journey filled with breathtaking action, intense emotions and larger-than-life characters. The film's release was nothing short of a festival, with fans celebrating in theaters around the world. We're humbled by the incredible response to the film and grateful to everyone who made it such a success. Here's to the power of storytelling and the magic of cinema!

#1ROCKYingYearOfKGF2

Written and Directed by Prashanth Neel
Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner "Hombale Films".
Starring: Rocking Star Yash, Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Prakash Raj, Malvika Avinash, Achyuth Kumar, Ayyappa P. Sharma, Rao Ramesh, Eshwari Rao, Archana Jois, T. S. Nagabharana, Saran, Avinash, Lakki Lakshman, Vashishta Simha, Harish Rai, Dinesh Mangalore, Tarak, Ramachandra Raju, Vinay Bidappa, Ashok Sharma, Mohan Juneja, Govinda Gowda, John Kokken, Srinivas Murthy.

Director of Photography: Bhuvan Gowda
Sound Design, Music & Background Score: Ravi Basrur
Co-director : Kirtan Nadagouda & Dhool Prakash
Direction Team: Bhargav N, Prashanth Hosmane, Chandan Bhargav, Yuvindraja, Nishanth Varma,  Muruli Muddenahally,Sanjay, Ghattimutthu Shashidhar, Abhijith Gorachi, Shiva Kumar, Mithilesh Gowda, Akash Thaargar, Akash Rambo, Roshan Sharif Farman Ullah.
Cameraman Team: Sandy, Prajwal Gowda, Kumar Gowda, Sagar Gowda, Manuraj  
Still - M G Narayan(Nani)
Executive Producer: Karthik Gowda, K. V Rama Rao
Editor: Ujwal Kulkarni
Production Design: Shivakumar
Action: Anbariv
Choreography: Harsha, Mohan
Dubbing: Anand Y. S
Costume Designer: Yogi G Raj, Sania Sardhariya, Navin Shetty, Ashwin Mawle, Hassan Khan
Dialogues: Chandramouli.M, Dr. Suri, Prashanth Neel
Sound Effects: Nanndhu J & Team
Production Managers: K S Champakadama,Gagan Murthy, S Kumar
Production Incharge: Chidanand, Suresh Shankarananhalli, Shashikanth
DI & VFX: Unify Media
VFX Supervisor: Konda Reddy Suresh
Colorist: Fergus Hally, Ashwath
Marketing: Likitha Reddy, Naren Marol, Anil Kumar, Shreya Unchalli, Suman, Sunith shetty, Adith, Sai pavan
PRO: Sudheendra Venkatesh (Kannada), Vamsi Kaka (Telugu), Yuvraaj (Tamil), Vivek Ramadevan (Malayalam)

snippet.title: Death Threats, Sidhu Moose Wala & SRK's Support - @YoYoHoneySingh  | Figuring Out | EP 85
snippet.description:
Order my first book 'Build, Don't Talk' here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu

--------------
In today’s episode of Figuring Out, Raj talks with Honey Singh, AKA Hirdesh Singh an Indian music producer, rapper, singer, songwriter and an actor and has been widely loved in the Hindi as well as Punjabi Film Industry. Hailing from Delhi,  Singh prefers to sing in Hindi and his native language Punjabii rather than English.

Singh shares how his life is a manifestation of what he wanted it to be like and how he’s been blessed to have received mentorship & support from the who’s who of the industry like Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan, Akshay Kumar, & Amitabh Bachchan. 

Honey Singh has finally broken his silence for the first time ever on ‘Mafia Mundeer’, a group of boys he made music with back in Punjab and the reasons behind breaking it off. 


Having gone through a tough journey of Bipolar Disorder, Singh speaks openly about dealing with mental illness, his symptoms, treatment and the struggle he went through during this time. 

Make sure you watch this video till the end!

snippet.title: ROUTINE (Official Video) Gur Sidhu | Jasmine Sandlas | Kaptaan | New Punjabi Song 2023 |Punjabi Song
snippet.description:
Brown Town Music & Nav Sandhu Presents New Punjabi Song Routine By Gur Sidhu Ft Jasmine Sandlas.

Listen to Routine song on all audio streaming platforms:

👉 Spotify: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/spotify

👉 Apple: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/appleMusic

👉 Wynk: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/wynk

👉 Amazon Music: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/amazonMusic

👉 Resso: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/resso

👉 YouTube Music: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/youtubeMusic

Track Credits:-
Song: Routine
Singer: Gur Sidhu Ft Jasmine Sandlas
Lyrics: Kaptaan
Music: Gur Sidhu
Mix & Master: B Sanjh
Concept / screenplay / direction: Garrybhullarfilms 
Dop - shoeb siddiqui 
Associate Director - Bunny khatri(Billa)
Editor - Garrybhullar 
Final Edit - Gobindpuriya 
BTS - Shubby 
Colorist - Onkar 
Vfx - Fury Vfx
Choreographer - Sumit 
Production House - Too Men 
Production Manager (rajasthan)- Himanshu Gupta
Promotion - Big Media
Instagram Promotions - Shine Media
Producer: Nav Sandhu
Label: Brown Town Music
Team Believe Artist Services: https://www.instagram.com/believeasd/


Team Gur Sidhu :
Hair - Abhishek 
Makeup  - Addy 
Costume  - Sruishty Juneja 

Team Jasmine Sandlas :
Hair - Ishan 
Makeup - Addy 
Costume - Priyana thappar
Management - Vaani Jindal

LYRICS:-

Main bathinde di cream te tu cali di queen ae
Krta scan billo jihnu kitta seen ae
Akh vich fire aa te cup ch caffine ae
Munda lagge zehar te tu lagdi zareen ae
Two face duniya imaan te na deen ae
Jo nal yakke turde aa ohna te yakeen ae
Golden kartoos russia di been ae
Khulli aa zmeen billo khulli beggy jean ae
Tuckin shirt aa te lagda shokeen ae

Ni ehtan sada regular mitthiye routine ae x4

Nakhro te noor poora husan hseen ae
Offran tan aoungiya kudi aafreen ae
Tim tim krdi ve age haale teen ae
Jhaaka mera jhaaka jatta surgan da scene ae
Scene j bnaunda jehda kr lainda seen ae
Dirty ja dekhda a teri ki skeem ae
Bhrr peg naina cho j lggea tu peen ae
Theke te na jayi meri akh di toheen ae

Munda....
Blue pinde label joint ch green ae

Ni ehtan sada.......

Ni ehtan sada
Ni ehtan sada

Ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

Kaptaan kaptaan kaptaan kaptaan nu
Harr koi firdi aa nal laike jaan nu
Ishqy crispy ja jatt dekh dekh k
Sohni ton v sohni pandi gabhru nu khaan nu

Puchde aa saare ve ah khand kitho ayi ae
Bnke poison di pand kitho ayi ae
Gol lakk nach nach vaal khull gye ve
Hoke taquilla nal band kitho ayi ae

Jatt vi oh chkke jihdi age eighteen ae

Ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

Kaatal queen mainu pyar nal aakh de
Mudke ni labbe kyi mere ch gwaach gye
Mera ki ksoor main v rabb ne bnaai aan
Kyi mainu dekh dekh vigad jwaak gye

Nazaran de nazran na paayi jaawe match ni
Aish cash lekhan ch tu karr farmaish ni
Ik do k habbitan khraab baby sadiyan
Peg vich ice aa te chaa ch black ni

Tu high off hoea firre hookeh da shokeen ae

Ni ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

#gursidhu #jasminesandlas #punjabisong 


For Licensing enquiries: 
Email:- sync-india@believedigital.com

#CheapvsExpensive #Foodiwe #Foodiwechallange

If you're a foodie, you won't want to miss this Cheap vs Expensive Food Challenge!  In this food challenge, we'll be testing cheap and expensive food #products and see which one is better in the eyes of the food critic!

This food challenge is perfect for food #lovers of all levels of price sensitivity. If you're looking for a challenging food challenge that will have you comparing prices and tastes, then this is the video for you!

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 32 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 32 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3745 - 14 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3745: Is The Coupon At Risk?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha assures Babita Ji that he will arrange the car for a day, but she must return it to him the next day for registration. Babita Ji is overjoyed at the news and praises Jetha for honoring her request. Jetha admires Bagha because it was his suggestion that led to Jetha obtaining the car from the Ramsang firm. Later, Bagha, Nattu Kaka, and Jetha begin to stamp the coupons, but the ink is accidentally spilled over them. Jetha becomes terrified when the coupon is spoiled. What happens next? Will Babita Ji now get the car? Keep watching to find out what happens next!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3745, 14 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: தமிழ் வருடப் பிறப்பு 2023 | சித்திரை கனி காணுதல் | வழிபடும் நேரம் & முறை | Tamil New Year 2023
snippet.description:
சித்திரை மாதத்தில் பிறந்தவர்களும், குழந்தை பெற்றவர்களும் பார்க்க வேண்டிய பதிவு | Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://youtu.be/XxAB_XVBMZo

மருத்து நீராடி தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை | கனி காணுதல் | தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு
https://youtu.be/0g00MJwEQNw

செல்வம், ஆரோக்கியம், நீண்ட ஆயுள் பெற தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை.   மேலும் கனி காணுதல், அறுசுவை உணவு படைத்தல், வழிபடும் நேரம் என பல தகவல்களை திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம் 

# சித்திரை கனி காணுதல் 
# தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு 
# Tamil New Year
# தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டு

Tere Bin Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 12th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3741 - Babita Wins a Car?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel.

आपको भी मिलेगा English की हर दिक्कत का Solution Josh पर  👇
https://joshskills.app.link/7RAyXfvuXyb

Venue Partner for this talk: Recreate Studio
Location: Mumbai

TV actress Roopal Tyagi was only 16 years old when she came to Bombay with the dream of becoming an actor. She has taught dance to big actors like Shahid Kapoor, Kareena Kapoor, Neha Dhupia, and Vidya Balan. Roopal Tyagi has also appeared in reality shows like Bigg Boss and khatron ke khiladi. After 11 consecutive Flop shows, she got a chance to work in a big TV show Sapne suhane ladakpan ke which became a very popular TV Serial. Roopal Tyagi had to face many difficulties after her relationship broke up. Lies were also published about her in the newspapers but she never gave up.

Today Roopal Tyagi will tell us her life story through Josh Talks that how she became a successful actor. So do watch this Hindi Motivational/Inspirational video of Josh Talks completely.

TV Actress Roopal Tyagi सिर्फ़ 16 साल की थी जब बॉम्बे में अपने Actor बनने के सपने के साथ आईं. इन्होंने Shahid Kapoor, Kareena Kapoor, Neha Dhupiya और Vidya Balan जैसे बड़े-बड़े Actors को Dance सिखाया है. Roopal Tyagi Bigg Boss और Khatron Ke Khiladi जैसे Reality Shows में भी आई हैं. लगातार 11 Flop Shows के बाद इन्हें एक बड़ा TV Show 'Sapne Suhane Ladakpan Ke' में काम करने का मौका मिला जो काफ़ी ज़्यादा Poppulor TV Serial बन गया. Roopal Tyagi के Relationship के टूट जाने के बाद इन्हें कईं मुश्किलों का सामना करना पड़ा. अखबारों में इनके बारे झूट भी छापा गया पर इन्होंने कभी हार नहीं मानी. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Roopal Tyagi हमें सुनायेंगी अपनी Life Story कि कैसे ये एक Successful Actor बनी. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi Motivational/inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें.  

#JoshTalksHindi #RoopalTyagiJoshTalks #RoopalTyagi #sapnesuhaneladakpanke #tvstar 

ऐसे ही Famous Actors और Bollywood Celebrities की Talks अभी देखें - 

Vishal Malhotra Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/ziYCMlg5VZo 
Anup Soni Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/wWDRAAArpkg
Actor Shyam Pathak Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/s8gIInusOmQ
Aasif Khan Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/ZHPYPpQvmXU
Sanjay Mishra Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/qJUDTxk8an8
Veebha Anand Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/fbgVjTYnyEg

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi...

Eredivisie 2022/2023 | ESPN NL
https://bit.ly/Eredivisie22-23
Voor alle content over het nieuwe Eredivisie seizoen 2022/2023 ben je bij deze afspeellijst op het goede adres. Wordt Ajax dit seizoen weer kampioen samen met de nieuwe trainer Alfred Schreuder? Of pakt Ruud van Nistelrooij in zijn eerste seizoen als hoofdtrainer de landstitel met PSV? En wat gaat Feyenoord dit seizoen doen? Dit seizoen zijn FC Emmen, Excelsior en FC Volendam nieuw in de hoogste Nederlandse voetbalcompetitie, dus ook hen zullen we veelvuldig in de gaten gaan houden. In deze playlist kijk je straks alle samenvattingen, highlights en unieke momenten van eredivisieclubs uit het eredivisieseizoen 22/23. Niets missen van het nieuwe seizoen? Ontdek de Eredivisie | ESPN NL
https://bit.ly/OntdekDeEredivisie
Ontdek de Eredivisie is een serie waarin Sjoerd Mossou de mooiste voetbalplekken van Nederland bezoekt voor ESPN. Meer te weten komen over de historie van Ajax? Of weten hoe de roots van Feyenoord, PSV en FC Twente eruit zien? Sjoerd Mossou gaat 20 voetbalclubs van Nederland af om de rijke historie te ontdekken. Wil jij meer te weten komen over jouw favoriete voetbalclub of juist van de aartsrivaal? Kijk dan in de afspeellijst van Ontdek de Eredivisie!
–
Welkom op het YouTube-kanaal van ESPN Nederland. ESPN is hét sportkanaal van Nederland en de plek waar je alles over voetbal vindt. Van Eredivisie voetbal met Ajax, PSV en Feyenoord tot Europa League voetbal, Conference League voetbal en alles over het meest actuele transfernieuws zoals de komst van Javairô Dilrosun, Steven Bergwijn en Guus Til. Ook alles over de Keuken Kampioen Divisie vind je op het ESPN Nederland YouTube kanaal.

Tijdens elke Eredivisie-speelronde vind je op ons kanaal samenvattingen die we binnen dertig minuten na het laatste fluitsignaal hebben geupload. Daarnaast vind je meerdere video’s per week met onder andere samenvattingen van Eredivisie en KKD wedstrijden, interviews met de beste voetbalspelers en de mooiste goals en grappigste fragmenten. snippet.title: अब आलू टिक्की व दही भल्ला इस तरह से बनायें, 1 ही डो से-Instant Aloo Sooji Tikki & Dahi Bhalla Chaat
snippet.description:
No-fry Bhalla Chaat step-by-step, Crispy Aloo ki Tikki, Instant Bhalla Chaat recipe, Instant Bhalla

#bhalla #steetfood #soojikanasta #chaat  

Ingredients for Sooji Aloo Tikki
तेल - Oil - 1 tsp
सूजी - Semolina - 1/2 cup (90 grams)
आलू - Potato - 5 pieces (350 grams)
नमक - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil - 2-3 tsp
जीरा - Cumin Seeds - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch
मटर - Pea - 1 cup
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/4 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/3 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dried mango powder - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander
तेल - Oil - 3-4 tbsp

Ingredients for Dahi Bhalla Chaat Chaat
दही - Curd
मीठी चटनी - Sweet sauce
तीखी चटनी - Chilli sauce
जीरा पाउडर - Cumin powder - Roasted
काला नमक - Black salt
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli
बूंदी - Boondi

snippet.description:

Ekam feels guilty for dragging Harleen through his mess and takes her out for lunch. He gets lost in his thoughts and abandons her at the restaurant. Will Harleen forgive him?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?
